        date: "2026.04.18 / Xiaohongshu",
        link: "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69e33599000000001f002aff?xsec_token=AByc9zK8xWszb_VHa3FCOZyPmzISzHpS-Ztq2rxDraKeI=&xsec_source=pc_user"
    },
    {
        title: "我的大学的老师们（大二版）",
        date: "2026.04.14 / Xiaohongshu",
        link: "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69ddb05c000000001e00fd94?xsec_token=ABWxKQ4tWPVDoS6z2A-cTIc_Hzw_B582tiHC_77Zv9nEE=&xsec_source=pc_user"
    },
    {
        title: "大学生活的“轻松与随便”毁了我",
        date: "2026.04.11 / Xiaohongshu",
        link: "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69d5a012000000001a02ed3b?xsec_token=ABfml7phlbjMa50f-w2urwz11SYkLQwbiVzZBbIIFXT0E=&xsec_source=pc_user"
    },
    {
        title: "浅谈大学水课和硬课",
        date: "2026.04.10 / Xiaohongshu",
        link: "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69cdb21a00000000230161d2?xsec_token=ABNG_OG1eRDnobAAYIQxHSm8mRqVY4N0JbgSHHJDv89Kc=&xsec_source=pc_user"
    },
    {
        title: "认知实习报告",
        date: "2026.04.09 / Xiaohongshu",
        link: "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69cccea9000000002301f579?xsec_token=ABEM7wm3Qo1rBWkSz1Y_xgM7b0aQC7dHO7Y67NnZz6V6o=&xsec_source=pc_user"
    },
    {
        title: "“你变了”和“我眼镜找不到了”的量子纠缠关系",
        date: "2026.04.08 / Xiaohongshu",
        link: "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69b9ea80000000001f001dc8?xsec_token=ABhuvVN7xXveC-Ghi8Vsj2ckE7DllgR0i-5vT8vhTz3EE=&xsec_source=pc_user"
